msg: Fix for log -g on a merged revision where a path got explicit mergeinfo
added when before the merge it had only inherited mergeinfo.
(fs_mergeinfo_changed): Account for the fact that when a revision
adds explicit mergeinfo to a path, that previously the path may
have inherited mergeinfo, rather than assuming it had no mergeinfo.
